<item>
            <title>[SPARK-24110] Avoid calling UGI loginUserFromKeytab in ThriftServer</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-24110</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Spark ThriftServer will call UGI.loginUserFromKeytab twice in initialization. This is unnecessary and will cause various potential problems, like Hadoop IPC failure after 7 days, or RM failover issue and so on.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So here we need to remove all the unnecessary login logics and make sure UGI in the context never be created again.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
